Murray Hamilton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Murray_Hamilton 0 Murray Hamilton (March 24, 1923 – September 1, 1986) was an American stage, screen, and television character actor who appeared in such films as Anatomy of a Murder, The Hustler, The Graduate, The Amityville Horror and Jaws.
